Subject: Justin T. Sisco, a Navy chief aviation machinist, stands beside a tree marking the boundary of a hastily established helicopter field at the Tampico Country Club which carries his name. U. S. Navy helicopters used this field as one of their bases for distributing food and mexical supplies to isolated Mexican people struck by Hurricane Janet.
